        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3357816161" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer710548809382968009">This book is dumb. The writing is not that great, the action scenes are overblown, and the conspiracy plot is ridiculous. The &quot;facts&quot; are incorrect, the science is misleading. But I can&apos;t get enough of these books. There&apos;s just something about the batshit craziness that goes on in these that I can&apos;t stop reading them. Next!</span>
  <span id="freeText710548809382968009" style="display:none">This book is dumb. The writing is not that great, the action scenes are overblown, and the conspiracy plot is ridiculous. The "facts" are incorrect, the science is misleading. But I can't get enough of these books. There's just something about the batshit craziness that goes on in these that I can't stop reading them. Next!</span>
